    Class
    Description
    Anime.Language
    Indicates the language used in the anime
    Media
    Defines a generic Media object with fields that are common between all entry types planned for the log project, including Anime, Manga, etc...
    Media.MediaType
    Indicates which type of media is involved, useful for when the class isn't visible and certain checks/behaviour need to be involved.
    Media.Type
    Indicates whether the content is a series, or a special.
    Preferences
    Container class for preference enums, related to Sorting and Color preferences
    Preferences.ColorMethod
    Indicates how the data is to be colored, if at all.
    Preferences.SortFocus
    Indicates whether the data is sorted by title (alphabetical) or by year (numerical).
